(42, 6, 26, 61, 2, 1, 3, 'false prophets', 'Connection of False Prophets', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of false prophets and their negative impact on the community. Luke warns against the approval of men that false prophets receive, while 2 Peter describes the destructive nature of their teachings and the consequences they bring.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
