(42, 6, 28, 59, 3, 10, 10, 'bless them that curse you', 'Blessing and Cursing Connection', 'This connection highlights the contrast between blessing and cursing in both passages. Luke emphasizes the call to bless those who curse, while James warns against the inconsistency of blessing and cursing from the same mouth.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
